y!  Queer Prom 2009!  See you at the National Museum of Mexican Art tonight @ 6pm','','','2009-05-29 15:06:04','2009-07-20 15:09:46'),(37,'1948381101','Queer Prom is tomorrow @ NMMA. Everybody is talking about what to wear.  Free makeup for youth after 4pm, http://tinyurl.com/qwwmso','','','2009-05-28 15:40:04','2009-07-20 15:09:46'),(38,'1940144913','Que tal les gusta el idea de tener un(a) locutor anunciando en ingles o en spanglish durante nuestra programacion en español?','','','2009-05-27 22:01:39','2009-07-20 15:09:46'),(39,'1937623135','Queer Prom this Friday. Free and anonymous HIV testing.  Free, professional make-up for youth Dress to Express http://tinyurl.com/qwwmso','','','2009-05-27 17:05:17','2009-07-20 15:09:46'),(40,'1937006759','Are you coming to Queer Prom this Friday? 6pm at NMMA. RSVP here http://bit.ly/2jJPh','','','2009-05-27 16:02:36','2009-07-20 15:09:46'),(41,'1936997520','http://bit.ly/2jJPh','','','2009-05-27 16:01:39','2009-07-20 15:09:46');
