com/on-the-gpl-themes-plugins-free/#comments\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Thu, 02 Jul 2009 19:23:04 +0000\";s:2:\"dc\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";s:13:\"Joost de Valk\";}s:8:\"category\";s:42:\"WordPressWordPress PluginsWordPress Themes\";s:4:\"guid\";s:48:\"http://yoast.com/on-the-gpl-themes-plugins-free/\";s:11:\"description\";s:762:\"So, we\'ve finally got an official word on this, the one sentence summary by Matt reads:\nPHP in WordPress themes must be GPL, artwork and CSS may be but are not required.\n\nOk, so that\'s the final truth, because the Software Freedom Law Center (who are of course absolutely NOT partial in this, even though they\'re called <p><a href=\"http://yoast.com/on-the-gpl-themes-plugins-free/\">On the GPL, Themes, Plugins &#038; Free.</a> is a post from <a href=\"http://yoast.com/about-me/\">Joost de Valk</a>&#39;s <a href=\"http://yoast.com/\">Yoast - Tweaking Websites</a>. \n\nA good blog needs good hosting, you don\'t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Use <a href=\"http://yoast.com/out/westhost/\">WestHost</a>, and you\'ll never have issues again!</p>\n\";s:7:\"content\";s:23:\"Array\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\";s:3:\"wfw\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentrss\";s:53:\"http://yoast.com/on-the-gpl-themes-plugins-free/feed/\";}s:5:\"slash\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";s:2:\"45\";}s:5:\"media\";a:2:{s:7:\"content\";s:24:\"\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\";s:13:\"content_title\";s:51:\"SphinnStumbleUponFacebookdel.icio.usLinkedInTwitter\";}s:10:\"feedburner\";a:1:{s:8:\"origlink\";s:95:\"http://yoast.com/on-the-gpl-themes-plugins-free/#utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=rss\";}s:7:\"summary\";s:762:\"So, we\'ve finally got an official word on this, the one sentence summary by Matt reads:\nPHP in WordPress themes must be GPL, artwork and CSS may be but are not required.\n\nOk, so that\'s the final truth, because the Software Freedom Law Center (who are of course absolutely NOT partial in this, even though they\'re called <p><a href=\"http://yoast.com/on-the-gpl-themes-plugins-free/\">On the GPL, Themes, Plugins &#038; Free.</a> is a post from <a href=\"http://yoast.com/about-me/\">Joost de Valk</a>&#39;s <a href=\"http://yoast.com/\">Yoast - Tweaking Websites</a>. \n\nA good blog needs good hosting, you don\'t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Use <a href=\"http://yoast.com/out/westhost/\">WestHost</a>, and you\'ll never have issues again!</p>\n\";s:12:\"atom_content\";s:1:\"A\";}i:9;a:15:{s:5:\"title\";s:29:\"Yet Another WordPress Podcast\";s:4:\"link\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/joostdevalk/~3/ntKeAykhon0/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:56:\"http://yoast.com/yet-another-wordpress-podcast/#comments\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Wed, 01 Jul 2009 20:58:33 +0000\";s:2:\"dc\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";s:13:\"Joost de Valk\";}s:8:\"category\";s:19:\"WordPresspodcastWMR\";s:4:\"guid\";s:47:\"http://yoast.com/yet-another-wordpress-podcast/\";s:11:\"description\";s:741:\"I\'ve just agreed with my buddy Daron Babin of WebmasterRadio.FM to be the host for a weekly WordPress podcast, no names or time slots decided yet but I\'m so excited about the news that I wanted to share it with you all!\nAll your suggestions for names, topics and guests are welcome in the comments!\nYet Another <p><a href=\"http://yoast.com/yet-another-wordpress-podcast/\">Yet Another WordPress Podcast</a> is a post from <a href=\"http://yoast.com/about-me/\">Joost de Valk</a>&#39;s <a href=\"http://yoast.com/\">Yoast - Tweaking Websites</a>. \n\nA good blog needs good hosting, you don\'t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Use <a href=\"http://yoast.com/out/westhost/\">WestHost</a>, and you\'ll never have issues again!</p>\n\";s:7:\"content\";s:30:\"Array\n			\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\";s:3:\"wfw\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentrss\";s:52:\"http://yoast.com/yet-another-wordpress-podcast/feed/\";}s:5:\"slash\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";s:2:\"19\";}s:5:\"media\";a:2:{s:7:\"content\";s:28:\"\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n		