m/~r/rss/cnn_topstories/~4/P-0UpiA62ic\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";}i:8;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:42:\"Capture of U.S. soldier \'breaks our heart\'\";s:4:\"guid\";s:102:\"http://www.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/asiapcf/07/20/afghanistan.soldier.hostage/index.html?eref=rss_topstories\";s:4:\"link\";s:66:\"http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/cnn_topstories/~3/lXfv5xZY6-E/index.html\";s:11:\"description\";s:1254:\"A family friend of a U.S. soldier captured by the Taliban said his friends and family want Pfc. Bowe Bergdahl to \"stand tall, stand firm.\"<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://rss.cnn.com/~ff/rss/cnn_topstories?a=lXfv5xZY6-E:rJBSCvyuKcY:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/rss/cnn_topstories?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://rss.cnn.com/~ff/rss/cnn_topstories?a=lXfv5xZY6-E:rJBSCvyuKcY:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/rss/cnn_topstories?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://rss.cnn.com/~ff/rss/cnn_topstories?a=lXfv5xZY6-E:rJBSCvyuKcY:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/rss/cnn_topstories?i=lXfv5xZY6-E:rJBSCvyuKcY:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://rss.cnn.com/~ff/rss/cnn_topstories?a=lXfv5xZY6-E:rJBSCvyuKcY:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/rss/cnn_topstories?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://rss.cnn.com/~ff/rss/cnn_topstories?a=lXfv5xZY6-E:rJBSCvyuKcY:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/rss/cnn_topstories?i=lXfv5xZY6-E:rJBSCvyuKcY:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/rss/cnn_topstories/~4/lXfv5xZY6-E\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:29:\"Mon, 20 Jul 2009 13:46:04 EDT\";s:10:\"feedburner\";a:1:{s:8:\"origlink\";s:102:\"http://www.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/asiapcf/07/20/afghanistan.soldier.hostage/index.html?eref=rss_topstories\";}s:7:\"summary\";s:1254:\"A family friend of a U.S. soldier captured by the Taliban said his frien